<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Concentration_of_media_ownership&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.cjr.org/resources/" class="external text" title="http://www.cjr.org/resources/" rel="nofollow">Who Owns What</a> by the <a href="/wiki/Columbia_Journalism_Review" title="Columbia Journalism Review">Columbia Journalism Review</a></li>
