<li><a href="http://www.neatorama.com/2008/07/07/who-owns-what-on-television/?%2F" class="external text" title="http://www.neatorama.com/2008/07/07/who-owns-what-on-television/?%2F" rel="nofollow">Who Owns What on Television</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.globalcitizen.co.uk/about/essays/mediaownership.doc" class="external text" title="http://www.globalcitizen.co.uk/about/essays/mediaownership.doc" rel="nofollow">Essay examining the reasons and consequences of media ownership</a>
<ul>
